step_data.thought: The previous actions have focused on ensuring the shopping cart is refreshed and verifying if the 'Qty' fields are editable. From the current page, we can observe that the 'Qty' fields are indeed editable, as they are represented by `spinbutton` elements. The user can proceed to adjust the quantities of the items in the cart as needed. The next action should be to inform the user that they can now edit the quantities of the items in their shopping cart.
step_data.action: stop('You can now edit the quantities of the items in your shopping cart. Simply adjust the values in the "Qty" fields and click "Update Shopping Cart" to apply your changes.')
